{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述寇仲与徐子陵在李世民船上，寇仲对李秀宁一见钟情，但李秀宁已与柴绍有婚约。李世民等人讨论突厥威胁与起兵计划。寇仲因失恋而立志要争霸天下，决定去荥阳寻找素素姐和李大哥，与徐子陵一同踏上新的旅程。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵！我有心上人了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你不觉得李小鬼的妹子长得很标致吗？既大方又温柔，那对眼秀而媚，胸脯玲珑浮凸，两条腿嘛，唉！包可把所有男人引死。脸蛋儿红扑扑的，肯定是这世上最可爱的脸蛋。皮肤则嫩滑如缎锦，白里透红。天啊！若能每晚都搂着她光脱脱的身子睡觉，我便不会再作他想，因这世上还有比这更惬意的事情吗？她说话的声音和神情才教人倾醉。，间中来个甜甜的微笑，横你娘的那么一眼，小陵啊！我快要爱死了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这就叫做爱吗？你这混蛋只是见色起心。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你不是常说娘儿愈多愈好吗？为何今趟只她一人便于愿已足。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不要翻我的旧账好吗？我说那种话时，只因我半个对象都没有，才以此豪语来安慰自己。现在有了她，自然就要专心一志。明白吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "看来你是认真的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "当然是认真的。现在李小鬼赶赴太原，迫他老子作反。凭李阀的声威，又有太原作基地，兵精粮足，大有机会做皇帝。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你对甚么他娘的义军仍不心灰吗？不若我们专心去走私盐发点乱世财，有了钱再帮助人，岂不胜过替人打生打死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "此一时彼一时也。嘿，你看看李小鬼那正义的模样，怎都像样过杜伏威、李密那些半人半鬼的家伙吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要说这些话了。说到底你只是想亲近李秀宁。不要怪我在你兴头上泼冰水。这贵家女表面虽似对我们客客气气的，但我总觉她有种拒我们于千里之外的味儿。像她这类高门大族出生的女儿家，绝不会看得上我们两个市井小流氓的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "人家第一次见到我们，仍是陌生，难道便纳你于方尺之内吗？这世上没有不可能的事。对娘儿自要用点心机和水磨功夫。待会李小子定会邀我们这两个有用的小鬼加入他的阵营，记着一切由我来说。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那谁去救素素姐呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你即使去追求你梦寐以求的秀宁小姐吧！素素姐就交由我负责好了。但我却绝不想加入任何一方的阵营，不过那本账薄却须取回来给我，好让我去给娘报仇。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寇兄、徐兄请坐，大家都是自己人了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位是裴寂先生，一手'忘形扇'会尽天下英豪，乃晋阳宫副监，家父的棋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "裴寂",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "世民侄过誉了，我那手跛脚鸭的功夫，怎拿得出来见人，更不要说会尽天下豪杰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "裴寂",
      "listener": "char_chai_shao",
      "text": "论功夫可要留给柴绍世侄去威风了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这是蒸胡饼，中间有羊肉葱白造的馅，以豉汁、芝麻和盐熬熟，非常美味。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chai_shao",
      "speaker_name": "柴绍",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "今趟世叔是不得不起兵，若起兵则必先取必中，就怕屈突通在蒲关和宋老生守霍邑的两支精兵，世叔看来不无顾忌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "裴寂",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "屈突通和宋老生固是可虑。但我担心的却是突厥人，其势日大。柬自契丹、室韦，西到吐谷浑、高昌等国均臣附之。且凡于北方起兵者，如刘武周、郭子和、梁师都等辈，无不依靠突厥而自立。我们进军关中时，最怕就是遭受突厥和刘武周等从后偷袭了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_pei_ji",
      "text": "这个无妨，力不足可以用诈，我现在唯一担心的事，就是爹他仍是犹豫不决，怕会坐失良机。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "裴寂",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "这事包在我裴寂身上。只要我和文静多下说辞，且眼前又确是形势危急，你爹那还有选择馀地呢？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟全赖两位，若不是账簿失窃，恐仍难营造出这种形势。最妙是那昏君刚巧到了江都应付杜伏威，此实千载一时之机。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chai_shao",
      "speaker_name": "柴绍",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "宁妹终于来了，为兄等得心都快要烧成火炭呢。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄是否身子不舒服呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "定是昨晚浸了湖水着凉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_chai_shao",
      "text": "昨晚秀宁见到他们时，还以为有两只小水鬼由湖里爬出来害人呢。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "没甚么？只因我除了是水鬼外，也是饿鬼，吃得太饱了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我只是打个譬喻，寇兄莫要见怪。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄是在说笑吧！嘿！昨晚那个到东溟号夺账簿的究竟是何方神圣呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chai_shao",
      "speaker_name": "柴绍",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "看来都不该是甚么厉害人物，否则寇兄和徐兄那能有机可乘。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_chai_shao",
      "text": "那人够胆子单枪匹马到高手如云的东溟号上偷东西，怎也该算有点斤两。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chai_shao",
      "speaker_name": "柴绍",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "他是趁东溟夫人和公主离船来会我们时才敢下手呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "琬晶姐若不是心切要见二哥，仍留在船上，就不会容那贼子偷袭得手，还伤了尚公哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "秀宁莫忘了我是有家室的人，但话也可反过来说，若非那人伤了尚公，我们亦休想得到夫人这至关紧要的一封书信。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "裴寂",
      "listener": "char_chai_shao",
      "text": "绍贤侄切莫小觊此人，只看他能打得尚公全无招架之力，可见后来虽给两位小兄弟夺去账簿，想来只是失诸轻敌吧！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_pei_ji",
      "text": "此人应是宇文阀的人，论水性，宇文阀内自以宇文成都排首位，不过该不会是他亲来，否则寇兄和徐兄就难以解开穴道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "我们兄弟希望能取回账簿好去办一件大事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_ji",
      "speaker_name": "裴寂",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这账簿关系到各方面与东溟派的兵器买卖，留在我们手上较为适合点。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若让人知道账簿在你们手上，只是东溟派巳绝不肯放过你们。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "这可是我们兄弟俩的事，李兄意下如何？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和两位一见投缘，若两位没有甚么地方非去不可，大可与我李世民同心合力闯他一闯，将来我李家有成，两位亦可享尽富贵。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "李兄的好意心领了。由于我们另有要事去办，只望李兄能把账簿还给我们，再随便把我们送上附近的岸边就成。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chai_shao",
      "speaker_name": "柴绍",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "这怎……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "假若我说不行，就是不够朋友和义气了。就依两位所说的办吧。但别忘了将来你们改变心意时，随时可再来找我李世民。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲少！你没有甚么吧？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我可以有甚么吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大丈夫何患无妻，何况仲少你今趟是非战之失，只是给那柴小鬼捷足先登吧了！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我情愿她恨我！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "就像东溟公主恨你般那样恨我，那起码我还可在她心中占个位置。但现在看她对我的离开毫不在意，根本上我们只是为她李阀奔走出力的两个小喽罗，连令她不欢喜的资格也欠奉。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我能比你好多少，你听不到那刁蛮公主只会看上李小鬼那种身分地位的人吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "很好笑吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我想通了，所以觉得很好笑。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快说出来听听。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若论才貌，我才不信我们会比李小鬼或柴小鬼差得多少。为何他们都不当我们是东酉呢？因为我们欠缺了成就。无论在江湖上又或社会间，没有成就的人都不会被重视。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "但若只是为了别人而去争取名利地位，那不是等若让人牵着鼻子走吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "说到底仍是为了自己，被人敬重只是随之而来的后果。大丈夫立身世上，若不能成就一番功业，让宝贵的生命白白溜走，岂不可惜。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今趟你又有甚么鬼主意呢？再不是要当盐商了吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我要当皇帝！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我寇仲要争霸天下，建立起万世不朽的功业。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "立志必须远大，做不成时，打个折扣还是有些儿斤两。今时再不同往日了，论才智，我们不比任何人差，论武功，我们欠的只是经验火候。现在我们先去荥阳找素素姐，假若能找到李大哥就更好。一世人两兄弟，你究竟帮不帮我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "来！让我们先比较脚力，再练习一下拳脚功夫，横竖我们连割肉刀都没半把，只好将就点。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 340
    }
  ],
